description: Try our easy to follow Prawn Laksa recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Prawn dishes,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,Prawn,Tree nut free,Egg free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Dairy free
name: Prawn Laksa Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500g green banana prawns, peeled and deveined

recipeInstructions.text: Place noodles into a large bowl and cover with boiling water. Stand for 10 minutes until soft.
Soak bean shoots and coriander in iced water and set aside.

Meanwhile, heat oil in a large saucepan. Add laksa paste and cook for 2 minutes until aromatic. Stir in coconut cream and stock and bring to the boil. Add snow peas, corn, carrot and prawns and reduce heat to medium. Cook for 3 minutes until prawns have changed colour.
Ladle over soup, prawns and vegetables.
Top with bean shoots and coriander and serve with a wedge of lime.
